573
00:26:35,125 --> 00:26:36,583
how to act in this play.

574
00:26:41,166 --> 00:26:43,625
No, saying it like this sounds way too arrogant.

575
00:26:53,125 --> 00:26:53,916
Chen Jing'an,

576
00:26:55,041 --> 00:26:55,833
Chen Jing'an,

577
00:26:56,583 --> 00:26:58,000
I know you're under a lot of stress.

578
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,875
But you mustn't let it get to you.

579
00:27:02,333 --> 00:27:03,458
You really mustn't let it get to you.

580
00:27:08,916 --> 00:27:09,541
Chen Changning,

581
00:27:09,791 --> 00:27:11,625
Can you go to the print shop with me?

582
00:27:13,500 --> 00:27:15,583
I want to print out the script for Romeo and Juliet.

583
00:27:15,625 --> 00:27:16,583
Print it out.

584
00:27:18,041 --> 00:27:19,041
Why print the script?

585
00:27:20,041 --> 00:27:21,666
Chen Jing'an is helping me with the play.

586
00:27:21,916 --> 00:27:23,625
But she's run into some trouble.

587
00:27:23,750 --> 00:27:24,833
I want to help her.

588
00:27:25,541 --> 00:27:26,458
Acting in a play?

589
00:27:26,958 --> 00:27:27,666
She's playing Juliet.

590
00:27:29,875 --> 00:27:30,833
Someone like Chen Jing'an

591
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:32,083
is only suited for comedy.

592
00:27:34,083 --> 00:27:34,583
Let's go.

593
00:28:04,625 --> 00:28:05,958
Is this play hard to perform?

594
00:28:06,458 --> 00:28:08,458
Jing'an doesn't have any experience acting in plays.

595
00:28:08,666 --> 00:28:10,416
This play also has a lot of lines.

596
00:28:10,625 --> 00:28:11,875
She has to memorize all of them.

597
00:28:11,958 --> 00:28:13,750
And she also needs to put emotion into it.

598
00:28:14,625 --> 00:28:16,750
That's pretty challenging for her.

599
00:28:17,208 --> 00:28:17,958
But

600
00:28:18,250 --> 00:28:19,458
I'll make good notes.

601
00:28:19,666 --> 00:28:21,625
I'll do my best to help her.

602
00:28:23,375 --> 00:28:24,750
Let me help Chen Jing'an rehearse.

603
00:28:27,208 --> 00:28:28,916
If you help Chen Jing'an with the male lines,

604
00:28:29,125 --> 00:28:29,916
she'll get distracted.

605
00:28:30,375 --> 00:28:31,166
Compared to you,

606
00:28:31,916 --> 00:28:33,625
my rehearsing with her will be much more efficient.

607
00:28:34,375 --> 00:28:35,583
She's acting in your role.

608
00:28:36,041 --> 00:28:37,250
You don't want her to mess up, right?

609
00:28:39,625 --> 00:28:40,750
But

610
00:28:40,875 --> 00:28:42,958
How should I tell Chen Jing'an?

611
00:28:44,958 --> 00:28:45,750
No need to say anything.

612
00:28:46,541 --> 00:28:47,416
I'll just go over there.

613
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:49,791
Alright.

614
00:28:51,333 --> 00:28:52,125
Thanks.

615
00:29:04,125 --> 00:29:05,125
I was just thinking,

616
00:29:05,708 --> 00:29:07,708
Jing'an is really lucky to have a brother like you.

617
00:29:27,333 --> 00:29:28,291
You did all of this.

618
00:29:31,250 --> 00:29:33,416
There are also some lines I recorded in here.

619
00:29:33,833 --> 00:29:35,666
If you can't control your emotions,

620
00:29:35,875 --> 00:29:36,916
you can refer to this.

621
00:29:38,833 --> 00:29:40,250
Isn't this my Walkman?

622
00:29:42,750 --> 00:29:43,291
What?

623
00:29:43,583 --> 00:29:45,416
Are you afraid I'll embarrass you by using your identity?

624
00:29:46,666 --> 00:29:47,458
Yes.

625
00:29:48,416 --> 00:29:50,833
You already embarrassed me at the last speech contest.

626
00:29:51,166 --> 00:29:51,875
No matter what you say this time,

627
00:29:51,875 --> 00:29:53,208
you can't mess up the competition.

628
00:29:53,208 --> 00:29:53,958
Do you understand?

629
00:29:54,250 --> 00:29:55,375
You really don't trust me that much?

630
00:29:55,375 --> 00:29:56,958
You think I can't do anything right, don't you?

631
00:29:57,500 --> 00:29:58,208
Jing'an,

632
00:29:58,583 --> 00:30:00,416
don't put too much pressure on yourself.

633
00:30:00,541 --> 00:30:02,750
This isn't something you're good at anyway.

634
00:30:02,916 --> 00:30:04,333
Just do your best.

635
00:30:05,041 --> 00:30:05,875
Besides,

636
00:30:06,083 --> 00:30:08,250
this was supposed to be my responsibility.

637
00:30:08,541 --> 00:30:09,625
The fact that you can help me

638
00:30:09,625 --> 00:30:11,208
already makes me very grateful.

639
00:30:12,916 --> 00:30:13,875
You're welcome.

640
00:30:16,583 --> 00:30:17,375
Actually,

641
00:30:17,791 --> 00:30:19,375
what you said to me last time,

642
00:30:19,375 --> 00:30:20,791
I've thought about it carefully.

643
00:30:21,916 --> 00:30:23,000
Many times,

644
00:30:23,125 --> 00:30:25,125
I really don't know how to refuse others.

645
00:30:25,791 --> 00:30:26,541
And I'm afraid to

646
00:30:26,541 --> 00:30:28,875
express my true feelings.

647
00:30:29,541 --> 00:30:31,208
I'll try to change that little by little.

648
00:30:34,500 --> 00:30:35,250
Actually,

649
00:30:35,666 --> 00:30:36,666
I was wrong too.

650
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:38,125
At that time,

651
00:30:38,125 --> 00:30:39,083
I was only thinking about myself.

652
00:30:39,125 --> 00:30:40,583
I didn't consider your feelings at all.

653
00:30:40,875 --> 00:30:41,666
I'm sorry.

654
00:30:42,583 --> 00:30:43,583
It's okay.

655
00:30:44,833 --> 00:30:45,541
So,

656
00:30:45,916 --> 00:30:47,208
does this mean we've made up?

657
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:50,916
I wasn't really mad at you anyway.

658
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:53,500
What I said back then was just out of anger.

659
00:30:53,541 --> 00:30:54,708
I regretted it as soon as I said it.

660
00:30:55,083 --> 00:30:57,208
Let's rehearse our lines together after school.

661
00:30:57,625 --> 00:30:58,708
At the next rehearsal,

662
00:30:58,833 --> 00:31:00,250
let's surprise everyone.

663
00:31:00,416 --> 00:31:00,916
Okay.

664
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:12,625
Chen Jing'an, how far have you gotten with your script?

665
00:31:13,333 --> 00:31:14,333
I've only written half.

666
00:31:15,625 --> 00:31:17,250
Nian Nian has a lot of hosting experience.

667
00:31:17,291 --> 00:31:18,625
Let's go find her after school.

668
00:31:18,625 --> 00:31:19,666
Have her take a look at your script.

669
00:31:19,708 --> 00:31:21,000
She can share some of her experience with you.

670
00:31:21,375 --> 00:31:22,541
She's right.

671
00:31:23,083 --> 00:31:25,000
You really should ask Zhu Nian Nian for help.

672
00:31:25,291 --> 00:31:27,625
That way, it'll be more interesting to compete with you.

673
00:31:28,416 --> 00:31:29,333
No need.

674
00:31:29,333 --> 00:31:31,041
I can write it myself.

675
00:31:32,708 --> 00:31:34,125
You're just an amateur newbie.

676
00:31:34,125 --> 00:31:35,750
Why aren't you more open to advice?

677
00:31:36,958 --> 00:31:37,708
Chen Jing'an.

678
00:31:38,166 --> 00:31:39,083
With Nian Nian guiding you,

679
00:31:39,083 --> 00:31:40,958
you might even get a good ranking.

680
00:31:42,833 --> 00:31:43,416
Okay.

681
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:45,291
I'll go find her later then.

682
00:31:46,416 --> 00:31:47,833
Then let her know for me.

683
00:31:47,875 --> 00:31:48,666
Whether it's her

684
00:31:48,666 --> 00:31:49,791
or her student,

685
00:31:50,041 --> 00:31:51,166
I'm sure to win.

686
00:31:55,333 --> 00:31:56,208
Don't worry about her.

687
00:31:56,250 --> 00:31:57,500
Just focus on writing your script.

688
00:31:57,666 --> 00:31:59,208
I'll go find Nian Nian next period.

689
00:31:59,208 --> 00:32:00,166
I'll let her know.

690
00:32:00,208 --> 00:32:02,041
Ask her to help you review it after school.

691
00:32:02,333 --> 00:32:03,291
And give you some suggestions.

692
00:32:04,416 --> 00:32:05,166
Actually,

693
00:32:05,166 --> 00:32:07,583
we have a rehearsal for the play after school.

694
00:32:09,166 --> 00:32:10,458
Just the two of you?

695
00:32:11,041 --> 00:32:11,708
Yeah.

696
00:32:36,708 --> 00:32:38,250
Can I join you?

697
00:32:38,916 --> 00:32:40,208
Probably not.

698
00:32:40,291 --> 00:32:42,208
Nian Nian only asked me to go.

699
00:32:45,875 --> 00:32:46,541
Looks like

700
00:32:46,666 --> 00:32:48,333
I've completely fallen out of favor.

701
00:32:59,625 --> 00:33:01,291
Do you love me?

702
00:33:01,791 --> 00:33:03,625
I know you'll definitely say yes.

703
00:33:04,333 --> 00:33:06,541
My dear, gentle Romeo.

704
00:33:06,666 --> 00:33:07,750
If you truly love me,

705
00:33:08,041 --> 00:33:09,625
then tell me sincerely.

706
00:33:15,708 --> 00:33:16,666
Why are you here?

707
00:33:18,166 --> 00:33:18,958
I'm here to rehearse.

708
00:33:20,791 --> 00:33:21,583
Rehearse what?

709
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:24,041
Romeo and Juliet.

710
00:33:29,708 --> 00:33:31,416
Chen Jing'an invited me to come and act with you.

711
00:33:33,875 --> 00:33:35,250
Then why didn't she tell me?

712
00:33:36,750 --> 00:33:37,541
Maybe she forgot.

713
00:33:38,583 --> 00:33:39,541
Then wait for her to come.

714
00:33:40,375 --> 00:33:41,375
And have her tell you again.

715
00:33:43,625 --> 00:33:44,416
Forget it.

716
00:33:45,250 --> 00:33:47,208
It's better to have someone to act with than no one.

717
00:33:48,041 --> 00:33:49,375
Then you play the male role.

718
00:33:49,541 --> 00:33:50,625
Read lines with me.

719
00:33:50,791 --> 00:33:51,583
Okay.

720
00:34:00,791 --> 00:34:02,708
Don't deny that you love me in front of him.

721
00:34:03,041 --> 00:34:05,000
I'm willing to admit in front of you that I love him.

722
00:34:06,833 --> 00:34:07,875
Your emotions here aren't right.

723
00:34:08,583 --> 00:34:10,166
This isn't how Juliet would speak.

724
00:34:10,791 --> 00:34:11,583
It's too harsh.

725
00:34:12,583 --> 00:34:14,416
But she's being forced into marriage right now.

726
00:34:14,625 --> 00:34:15,875
She loves Romeo so much.

727
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:19,208
And Paris is so annoying, isn't he?

728
00:34:21,166 --> 00:34:22,291
Can't she be a little harsh?

729
00:34:23,583 --> 00:34:24,833
Juliet is a noble lady.

730
00:34:25,583 --> 00:34:26,916
Even if she resists the engagement,

731
00:34:27,375 --> 00:34:28,791
she wouldn't act so rude.

732
00:34:29,625 --> 00:34:31,000
Then what's the point of acting it out?

733
00:34:31,041 --> 00:34:32,333
When facing someone you really dislike,

734
00:34:32,625 --> 00:34:33,625
you still have to be polite.

735
00:34:33,625 --> 00:34:35,041
If the audience doesn't feel frustrated, I do.

736
00:34:35,750 --> 00:34:36,750
So for you,

737
00:34:38,416 --> 00:34:39,750
if you're rude to someone,

738
00:34:40,833 --> 00:34:41,916
it's because you dislike them?

739
00:34:42,041 --> 00:34:42,791
What else could it be?

740
00:34:42,791 --> 00:34:43,750
Should I stand in front of him and say,

741
00:34:43,750 --> 00:34:44,625
"I like you"?

742
00:34:47,625 --> 00:34:48,583
Why are you telling me this?

743
00:34:48,583 --> 00:34:49,750
Aren't we discussing the script?

744
00:34:55,041 --> 00:34:56,291
An'an, you finally made it.

745
00:34:56,458 --> 00:34:57,583
Why did you call your brother here?

746
00:34:57,625 --> 00:34:59,458
He just gives random directions and makes things worse.

747
00:35:00,500 --> 00:35:01,583
Sorry.

748
00:35:01,833 --> 00:35:03,833
But Tian Ye and the others are also rehearsing.

749
00:35:03,958 --> 00:35:05,375
I had no choice but to ask him.

750
00:35:10,208 --> 00:35:11,625
I’m not blaming you.

751
00:35:11,833 --> 00:35:12,583
It’s just that—

752
00:35:12,958 --> 00:35:14,125
When he plays Romeo like that and says,

753
00:35:14,125 --> 00:35:15,291
"Let’s run away together,"

754
00:35:16,125 --> 00:35:17,708
I don’t find it romantic at all.

755
00:35:18,125 --> 00:35:19,541
All I want to do is call the police.

756
00:35:19,708 --> 00:35:21,000
Officer, please save me.

757
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:23,625
Am I that scary?

758
00:35:23,625 --> 00:35:24,500
Very scary.

759
00:35:25,291 --> 00:35:27,083
For the sake of a successful performance,

760
00:35:27,208 --> 00:35:28,500
can you just bear with it for now?

761
00:35:33,958 --> 00:35:34,583
Alright then.

762
00:35:35,041 --> 00:35:36,333
I'll do you this favor.

763
00:35:36,916 --> 00:35:38,125
Rehearse with him.

764
00:35:38,708 --> 00:35:39,708
We don't have much time.

765
00:35:39,708 --> 00:35:41,166
Let's hurry and rehearse.

766
00:35:41,583 --> 00:35:43,208
Let's rehearse the farewell scene first.

767
00:35:43,208 --> 00:35:44,583
That scene is quite important.

768
00:35:44,791 --> 00:35:45,250
Okay.

769
00:35:45,500 --> 00:35:46,000
Alright.

770
00:35:50,416 --> 00:35:52,041
Let the daylight come in.

771
00:35:52,041 --> 00:35:53,375
Let life go out.

772
00:35:54,208 --> 00:35:55,000
Farewell.

773
00:35:55,416 --> 00:35:56,041
Farewell.

774
00:35:57,250 --> 00:35:58,208
Give me a kiss.

775
00:35:58,750 --> 00:35:59,708
Then I'll leave.

776
00:36:00,500 --> 00:36:02,083
Are you leaving just like this, my husband?

777
00:36:03,958 --> 00:36:04,875
Wait a moment.

778
00:36:06,541 --> 00:36:07,416
Where did it go wrong?

779
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:08,875
I think

780
00:36:08,875 --> 00:36:10,875
the way you deliver your lines so stiffly

781
00:36:10,875 --> 00:36:12,375
is a bit too unnatural.

782
00:36:13,333 --> 00:36:14,375
But you two

783
00:36:14,625 --> 00:36:16,500
are playing lovers right now.

784
00:36:16,625 --> 00:36:18,875
Even ordinary friends would hug when parting.

785
00:36:19,416 --> 00:36:21,125
Otherwise, it looks too fake.

786
00:36:21,250 --> 00:36:23,291
The audience might criticize it.

787
00:36:26,125 --> 00:36:27,541
But we can't hug either.

788
00:36:28,791 --> 00:36:29,583
It's so awkward.

789
00:36:30,791 --> 00:36:31,708
Holding hands is fine too.

790
00:36:33,208 --> 00:36:34,958
Let's try it this way first.

791
00:36:42,666 --> 00:36:43,458
Don't move.

792
00:36:44,125 --> 00:36:44,916
Say your lines.

793
00:36:50,416 --> 00:36:51,166
Then

794
00:36:51,541 --> 00:36:52,333
goodbye

795
00:36:53,916 --> 00:36:54,708
my

796
00:36:55,208 --> 00:36:56,000
friend

797
00:36:57,791 --> 00:36:58,583
husband

798
00:36:58,875 --> 00:36:59,875
my beloved

799
00:37:03,166 --> 00:37:04,000
I will see you again

800
00:37:04,583 --> 00:37:05,375
my beloved

801
00:37:05,750 --> 00:37:07,458
I will never give up any chance

802
00:37:08,583 --> 00:37:09,875
to express my true feelings to you
